{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 53,
  "title": "第五十三章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "使我介然有知，行於大道，唯施是畏。"
    },
    {
      "text": "大道甚夷，而民好徑。"
    },
    {
      "text": "朝甚除，"
    },
    {
      "text": "田甚蕪，倉甚虛；"
    },
    {
      "text": "服文綵，帶利劍，厭飲食，財貨有餘；是為盜夸。非道也哉！"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言若使我可介然有知，行大道於天下，唯施為之是畏也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言大道蕩然正平，而民猶尚舍之而不由，好從邪徑，況復施為以塞大道之中乎。故曰，大道甚夷，而民好徑。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "朝，宮室也。除，潔好也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "朝甚除，則田甚蕪，倉甚虛，設一而眾害生也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 27
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "凡物不以其道得之，則皆邪也，邪則盜也。夸而不以其道得之，竊位也，故舉非道以明非道，則皆盜夸也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
